- cs.SC (Symbolic Computation) is possible because the paper deals with irregular computation patterns and sparsity structures, which may involve symbolic computations.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is possible because the paper discusses implementing tensor decomposition algorithms and optimizing GPU-specific optimizations.
